Job Details
Job Responsibility: Candidate should promote Wear Resistant Plates/Pipes/Fabricated components made out of Wear Resistant Plates/Pipes (Weld Cladded ) and Vertical Roller Mill Roller and Table Liner rebuilding.Candidate should handle the territory independently,generate enquiries and convert in to orders. To conduct seminars in cement plants, Power plants, Mining,etc., Report to Area Sales Manager based in Dubai.
Requirements
Experience: 6-8 years , preferably a person should have an experience in this territory, knowledge and exposure in cement plant and welding field background experienceLocal Language Speaking Candidate would be an added advantage and given preference.
